It's too cold. I don't want it.

270
00:14:37,890 --> 00:14:39,150
Will you take it or not?

271
00:14:44,700 --> 00:14:45,680
I'm sick,

272
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:48,120
but my girlfriend yelled at me

273
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,120
and called me Mr. Liu.

274
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,890
I'm too sad to take the medicine.

275
00:14:53,920 --> 00:14:55,790
Let me kindly remind you of this.

276
00:14:56,700 --> 00:14:58,230
You're still on probation.

277
00:14:58,880 --> 00:15:01,410
It just means that I'm your future boyfriend.

278
00:15:04,010 --> 00:15:04,410
Okay.

279
00:15:05,300 --> 00:15:06,100
In the future,

280
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:08,580
I'll call you Xilai.

281
00:15:10,620 --> 00:15:11,160
But

282
00:15:11,410 --> 00:15:13,940
I still need to call you Mr. Liu in the company.

283
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:27,950
Since Mr…

284
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:34,010
Since you've taken your medicine,

285
00:15:34,010 --> 00:15:35,250
I'll go back to the office.

286
00:15:35,250 --> 00:15:36,780
I'll leave you to your work.

287
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:40,450
Tian,

288
00:15:41,350 --> 00:15:43,010
I haven't eaten anything yet.

289
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:44,820
You want me to work now?

290
00:15:45,480 --> 00:15:46,750
So cruel.

291
00:15:47,990 --> 00:15:49,500
He's whining.

292
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:50,790
So cute.

293
00:15:55,250 --> 00:15:55,760
Okay.

294
00:15:56,380 --> 00:15:57,980
I'll make breakfast for you.

295
00:16:22,450 --> 00:16:23,040
Xilai,

296
00:16:23,570 --> 00:16:25,530
this is your healthy breakfast.

297
00:16:27,710 --> 00:16:29,080
Sit down and eat with me.

298
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:39,760
I wish

299
00:16:40,850 --> 00:16:42,450
time can stop at this moment.

300
00:16:43,820 --> 00:16:45,350
You don't have to go abroad.

301
00:16:52,670 --> 00:16:53,660
Don't run too fast.

302
00:16:53,660 --> 00:16:54,990
It's bad for your knees.

303
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,070
Drink more water.

304
00:16:56,070 --> 00:16:57,330
Don't get dehydrated.

305
00:16:57,780 --> 00:16:59,580
Why did you follow me here again?

306
00:16:59,590 --> 00:17:00,720
Are you that free?

307
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:04,859
Given that you just broke up and are heartbroken,

308
00:17:04,859 --> 00:17:06,119
I won't argue with you.

309
00:17:06,579 --> 00:17:07,040
Tell me.

310
00:17:07,599 --> 00:17:09,920
Do you want to go shopping or go to an art exhibition?

311
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,410
I'm all yours.

312
00:17:12,099 --> 00:17:13,780
I'm not heartbroken.

313
00:17:13,819 --> 00:17:14,880
It's just that you…

314
00:17:20,869 --> 00:17:21,780
I'm done running.

315
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:23,380
I'm going back to the studio.

316
00:17:28,770 --> 00:17:30,570
It isn't me who broke your heart.

317
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:32,640
Why are you avoiding me?

318
00:17:34,370 --> 00:17:36,230
Do you still feel uncomfortable?

319
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:39,660
But the fever has been brought down.

320
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,230
