330
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:16,210
This is the new AI toy

331
00:18:16,580 --> 00:18:18,760
developed by our company.

332
00:18:19,810 --> 00:18:22,500
It can talk with you anytime

333
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,140
and sing with you as well.

334
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:25,140
Do you want to try?

335
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:31,370
Miss Qian, do you want to chat?

336
00:18:31,910 --> 00:18:33,710
You can chat with the new AI robot

337
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:36,140
developed by my company.

338
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,460
It can chat with you anytime.

339
00:18:40,850 --> 00:18:42,360
Karma prevails.

340
00:18:42,780 --> 00:18:44,340
No one is an exception.

341
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:46,660
Everything is fate.

342
00:18:47,120 --> 00:18:48,760
There's nothing you can do.

343
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:52,880
Tian.

344
00:18:53,780 --> 00:18:54,220
I…

345
00:18:55,220 --> 00:18:56,620
My head hurts more badly.

346
00:18:57,140 --> 00:18:58,740
