351
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:19,300
Okay.

352
00:19:19,860 --> 00:19:21,260
What do you want to watch?

353
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,040
This one.

354
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:32,550
You make my heart smile.

355
00:19:35,180 --> 00:19:37,160
A big boss like you

356
00:19:37,600 --> 00:19:40,000
