357
00:19:43,080 --> 00:19:44,200
Fine.

358
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:45,620
Let's watch it.

359
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:48,180
You're sick. You make the decisions.

360
00:20:18,100 --> 00:20:18,630
How about

361
00:20:19,120 --> 00:20:21,630
we watch something else?

362
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:22,970
Tian,

363
00:20:23,460 --> 00:20:24,970
I think this one is good.

364
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:27,280
When you really love someone,

365
00:20:27,540 --> 00:20:30,350
you can't help

366
00:20:32,490 --> 00:20:33,720
but want to kiss her.

367
