370
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:54,730
Let's stop watching TV

371
00:20:54,730 --> 00:20:55,610
and take a rest.

372
00:20:58,710 --> 00:20:59,470
But...

373
00:21:00,910 --> 00:21:02,210
we are not kids.

374
00:21:13,850 --> 00:21:15,510
Why did you take off your watch?

375
00:21:15,510 --> 00:21:16,640
It's a little tight.

376
00:21:24,450 --> 00:21:26,250
Why did you unbutton your shirt?

377
00:21:26,460 --> 00:21:27,460
It's a little hot.

378
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,070
What are you doing?

379
00:21:38,060 --> 00:21:39,190
You're still sick.

380
00:21:45,060 --> 00:21:45,630
Tian,

381
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:51,960
I have something to tell you.

382
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:56,120
What is it?

383
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,140
Can you

384
00:22:01,020 --> 00:22:01,660
stay?

385
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:04,460
Can you not go abroad…

386
00:22:07,150 --> 00:22:08,370
(Senior)

387
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:18,840
That playboy

388
00:22:19,520 --> 00:22:21,920
is so good at messing things up.

389
00:22:22,220 --> 00:22:23,080
Hello, senior.

390
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:25,560
I haven't booked the flight yet.

391
00:22:25,890 --> 00:22:27,220
Choose your seat first.

392
00:22:29,230 --> 00:22:31,420
I don't want to give you freedom anymore.

393
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:32,700
I can't give Tian the opportunity

394
00:22:32,700 --> 00:22:33,900
to bond with my rival.

395
00:22:34,950 --> 00:22:35,900
Three months.

396
00:22:36,370 --> 00:22:38,560
Who knows

397
00:22:38,610 --> 00:22:39,610
what will happen.

398
00:23:27,130 --> 00:23:28,300
No!

399
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:31,190
I can't let that happen.

400
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:33,890
Okay.

401
00:23:34,640 --> 00:23:35,280
I see.

402
00:23:36,370 --> 00:23:36,770
Bye.

403
00:23:41,570 --> 00:23:42,370
What's wrong?

404
00:23:42,850 --> 00:23:44,110
Why do you look so pale?

405
00:23:44,490 --> 00:23:45,180
Tian.

406
00:23:45,940 --> 00:23:47,220
I feel tightness in my chest.

407
00:23:47,220 --> 00:23:47,950
I feel so bad.

408
00:23:48,950 --> 00:23:49,790
What's wrong?

409
00:23:51,450 --> 00:23:51,740
Sit.

410
00:23:52,350 --> 00:23:53,610
You were fine just now.

411
00:23:57,710 --> 00:23:59,240
Has your cold got worse?

412
00:23:59,630 --> 00:24:00,440
I…

413
00:24:01,230 --> 00:24:02,270
I feel dizzy now

414
00:24:03,350 --> 00:24:05,280
as if I'd been struck by lightning.

415
00:24:05,380 --> 00:24:06,900
Dizzy?

416
00:24:08,650 --> 00:24:10,310
Has his hemophobia relapsed?

417
00:24:15,340 --> 00:24:16,670
Are you still dizzy now?

418
00:24:18,900 --> 00:24:20,900
I'm fine as long as you're by my side.

419
00:24:21,290 --> 00:24:23,150
Once I think that you'll leave me,

420
00:24:23,580 --> 00:24:26,040
my heart aches so badly that I can't breathe.

421
00:24:26,300 --> 00:24:28,490
Is it because of your hemophobia?

422
00:24:29,210 --> 00:24:30,940
Why did it relapse so suddenly?

423
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:32,310
She misunderstood.

424
00:24:33,470 --> 00:24:34,380
Hemophobia?

425
00:24:35,460 --> 00:24:38,280
Is God giving me a chance?

426
00:24:40,330 --> 00:24:40,790
Junior,

427
00:24:41,250 --> 00:24:43,180
how about we both take this flight?

428
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:45,870
We can sit together and take care of each other.

429
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:46,980
Take care?

430
00:24:47,630 --> 00:24:49,760
I don't need you to take care of my girl!

431
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:53,380
Tian,

432
00:24:54,220 --> 00:24:55,900
I can't live without you.

433
00:24:56,490 --> 00:24:59,160
I think the whole house is red now.

434
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:01,270
My head is spinning.

435
00:25:02,130 --> 00:25:04,390
Your hemophobia seems to have got worse.

436
00:25:05,330 --> 00:25:05,680
No.

437
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:07,880
I'll take you to see Dr. Li now.

438
00:25:07,940 --> 00:25:08,400
Li Huai.

439
00:25:10,260 --> 00:25:10,810
No need.

440
00:25:11,910 --> 00:25:13,310
I just need you by my side.

441
00:25:17,910 --> 00:25:18,650
Dr. Li.

442
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:20,760
Everything he sees now is red.

443
00:25:21,330 --> 00:25:24,220
Has his hemophobia got worse?

444
00:25:25,670 --> 00:25:26,510
Worse?

445
00:25:34,330 --> 00:25:34,870
Well,

446
00:25:35,060 --> 00:25:36,390
whether it's got worse,

447
00:25:36,620 --> 00:25:38,540
we'll know after I give him

448
00:25:38,850 --> 00:25:40,170
further examination.

449
00:25:40,450 --> 00:25:41,050
Miss Tian,

450
00:25:41,490 --> 00:25:43,460
please wait outside.

451
00:25:51,060 --> 00:25:52,400
Do you have to go to such lengths

452
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:53,660
to make Miss Tian stay?

453
00:25:57,650 --> 00:25:59,110
I didn't mean to lie to her.

454
00:25:59,290 --> 00:26:01,820
Tian mistakenly thought that I had a relapse.

455
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:03,110
I just chose

456
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:05,360
not to explain.

457
00:26:05,770 --> 00:26:06,490
But,

458
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:07,840
Miss Tian

459
00:26:08,460 --> 00:26:10,540
really wants to go abroad for training, doesn't she?

460
00:26:10,540 --> 00:26:12,700
There is training abroad every year.

461
00:26:12,880 --> 00:26:14,510
But after Tian

462
00:26:14,550 --> 00:26:15,840
spends three months abroad

463
00:26:15,840 --> 00:26:17,870
with Luo Ci alone,

464
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:19,530
I may lose her forever.

465
00:26:21,430 --> 00:26:22,830
This is a special matter.

466
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:24,120
I want no part in it.

467
00:26:29,780 --> 00:26:30,430
Dude,

468
00:26:30,730 --> 00:26:33,610
my happiness lies in your decision.

469
00:26:39,070 --> 00:26:40,550
Then just tell Miss Tian

470
00:26:40,610 --> 00:26:42,240
that you don't want her to go abroad

471
00:26:42,240 --> 00:26:42,870
with Mr. Luo.

472
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:43,750
I can't say it.

473
00:26:44,470 --> 00:26:45,040
Besides,

474
00:26:45,470 --> 00:26:47,350
Luo Ci is just a playboy.

475
00:26:47,370 --> 00:26:49,050
Making me an option like him

476
00:26:49,410 --> 00:26:50,470
is not acceptable.

477
00:26:50,730 --> 00:26:52,860
It has always been me choosing others.

478
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:53,840
Besides,

479
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:56,110
what if I get rejected?

480
00:26:59,750 --> 00:27:00,650
I can't believe

481
00:27:01,050 --> 00:27:03,660
Liu Xilai, who has always been so conceited,

482
00:27:04,020 --> 00:27:05,590
is feeling so insecure now.

483
00:27:05,980 --> 00:27:08,710
I just don't want to waste the chance given by God.

484
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:11,520
I'll seal the car door

485
00:27:11,720 --> 00:27:12,920
so Tian can't get off.

486
00:27:13,670 --> 00:27:16,200
After I officially become Tian's boyfriend,

487
00:27:17,130 --> 00:27:19,610
I'll spend a fortune to hire the elites in this industry

488
00:27:19,610 --> 00:27:21,060
to be Tian's teachers.

489
00:27:33,680 --> 00:27:34,740
Miss Tian, come in.

490
00:27:38,850 --> 00:27:40,220
Dr. Li, how is he?

491
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:44,970
Is it serious?

492
00:27:51,260 --> 00:27:52,340
Xilai's condition

493
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:54,590
can be greatly affected by his mood.

494
00:27:54,730 --> 00:27:55,900
As his friend,

495
00:27:56,190 --> 00:27:58,390
I'm very grateful for your presence in his life.

496
00:27:58,390 --> 00:28:00,730
You made his life more colorful.

497
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,370
More importantly,

498
00:28:02,400 --> 00:28:04,000
you made him a normal person.

499
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:06,430
Why do you sound

500
00:28:06,460 --> 00:28:07,660
so grave?

501
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:11,010
I don't know what happened between you two,

502
00:28:11,010 --> 00:28:12,780
but you are indeed the first person

503
00:28:12,780 --> 00:28:14,580
who helped him get over his past.

504
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:15,690
This relapse

505
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:21,470
is caused by emotional reasons too.

506
00:28:21,470 --> 00:28:23,150
Maybe something you did

507
00:28:23,530 --> 00:28:24,880
made him insecure

508
00:28:25,390 --> 00:28:26,850
and caused him to fall ill.

509
00:28:27,740 --> 00:28:29,320
Something I did?

510
00:28:31,900 --> 00:28:32,570
Miss Tian,

511
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:33,580
as I said,

512
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:35,790
you're the only one who can help him.

513
00:28:35,810 --> 00:28:37,280
You need to find out

514
00:28:37,950 --> 00:28:40,080
the reason why he's feeling insecure.

515
00:28:40,270 --> 00:28:40,940
Me?

516
00:28:43,560 --> 00:28:44,170
Tian,

517
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:46,270
Dr. Li means

518
00:28:46,670 --> 00:28:48,540
your company is my cure.

519
00:28:49,330 --> 00:28:51,260
I need you to spend more time with me

520
00:28:51,510 --> 00:28:52,570
and take care of me.

521
00:28:52,980 --> 00:28:53,980
Am I right, Dr. Li?

522
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,540
Well,

523
00:28:57,730 --> 00:29:00,060
you can also find out what's bothering him

524
00:29:00,060 --> 00:29:01,660
and bring him to face his fear

525
00:29:01,850 --> 00:29:03,050
so he can overcome it.

526
00:29:03,870 --> 00:29:04,800
What do you mean?

527
00:29:07,380 --> 00:29:09,330
I'm telling Miss Tian what to do

528
00:29:09,520 --> 00:29:11,180
to make you get better sooner.

529
00:29:11,610 --> 00:29:13,070
Face the fear?

530
00:29:14,410 --> 00:29:14,980
Dr. Li,

531
00:29:15,300 --> 00:29:16,100
I understand.

532
00:29:17,300 --> 00:29:18,230
You understand?

